[11.385549, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[36m  ╔══════════════════════════════════ 🛡️  Proof-of-Audit ══════════════════════════════════╗\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m  ║ \u001b[0m                                                                                      \u001b[36m ║\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m  ║ \u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[32m  Lifecycle complete\u001b[0m                                                                  \u001b[36m ║\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m  ║ \u001b[0m                                                                                      \u001b[36m ║\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m  ║ \u001b[0m  \u001b[33mdraft\u001b[0m → \u001b[36mpublished\u001b[0m → \u001b[35mchallenged\u001b[0m → \u001b[32mresolved\u001b[0m                                           \u001b[36m ║\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m  ║ \u001b[0m                                                                                      \u001b[36m ║\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m  ║ \u001b[0m\u001b[97m  The judgment was stake-backed, challenged with evidence,\u001b[0m                            \u001b[36m ║\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m  ║ \u001b[0m\u001b[97m  and resolved transparently on-chain.\u001b[0m                                                \u001b[36m ║\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m  ║ \u001b[0m                                                                                      \u001b[36m ║\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m  ║ \u001b[0m\u001b[2m\u001b[3m  Trust comes from visible economic commitment.\u001b[0m                                       \u001b[36m ║\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m  ║ \u001b[0m                                                                                      \u001b[36m ║\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m  ║ \u001b[0m\u001b[2m\u001b[36m  ─── Live on Base Sepolia ───\u001b[0m                                                        \u001b[36m ║\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m  ║ \u001b[0m\u001b[2m  Contract: 0xf2dA…F24 · sepolia.basescan.org\u001b[0m                                         \u001b[36m ║\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m  ║ \u001b[0m                                                                                      \u001b[36m ║\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[36m  ╚════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
